Class AppendTableCompactSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.flink.source.AbstractNonCoordinatedSource<AppendCompactTask>
      • org.apache.paimon.flink.source.AppendTableCompactSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.apache.flink.api.connector.source.Source<AppendCompactTask,SimpleSourceSplit,NoOpEnumState>, org.apache.flink.api.connector.source.SourceReaderFactory<AppendCompactTask,SimpleSourceSplit>

    public class AppendTableCompactSource
extends AbstractNonCoordinatedSource<AppendCompactTask>
    Source for unaware-bucket Compaction.

    Note: The function is the source of unaware-bucket compactor coordinator. It will read the latest snapshot continuously by compactionCoordinator, and generate new compaction tasks. The source is used in unaware-bucket compaction job (both stand-alone and write-combined). Besides, we don't need to save state in this source, it will invoke a full scan when starting up, and scan continuously for the following snapshot.
